external_knowledge:
- "Shines the brightest" is a metaphorical expression referring to the stock with the best performance; 
- "Still on the access list" refers to the condition ua.expires_at > CURRENT_DATE, which filters out users whose access has expired; 
- "Best performing stock of the year 2023" refers to the stock with the highest rank based on its percent_change and confidence_score.

- Percentage change in price refers to the difference in price from the previous day, expressed as a percentage; 
- Top 3 stocks for each user refer to the stocks with the highest percentage change in price; 
- The date corresponds to the day when the price change occurred.

sql:
SELECT stock_name 
FROM stocks 
WHERE stock_id = 0;
